                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-248-off1270 t18280911-248-cd1271"></join>, 1 reticule, value 1s.; 1 scent-bottle, value 6d.; 1 thimble, value 6d.; 1 handkerchief, value 1s.; 1 sovereign, and 10 shillings, the property of 
